"Hmm?
Was there something in the shadows of that bush just now?"
"...I feel like I saw something in the shadows of that bush a second ago."

"Hoo hoo hoo. Are you planning to hide behind that bush?
Is there something inside that bush?"

"Oh, what?
Did I see something moving in that bush, you ask?"
"Hmm. I do sense something strange...Where is it?　Where is it coming from?"

"Could it just be the shadow of that bush?
It moved a bit just now."

"...This feeling. Is it coming from that bush?
It doesn't feel like it would be anything worth our time anyway."

"む？
今、茂みの陰に何かが居たな？"

"……今、茂みの中に
何か居たような気がする。"

"ふふふ、あれで隠れてる
つもりなんですかねえ？
茂みの中に、誰かいませんかあ？"

"おっ、なんだ？
あの茂み、今動かなかったか？"

"んー、なにやらヘンな気配……
どこだー？　どこからだー？"

"あの茂みの陰じゃないかな。
さっき、ちょっと動いてたし。"

"……この気配、そこの茂みかしら？
あんまり大物じゃなさそうだけど。"
